description: Soil sample consisting of a coherent, consolidated mass from a variable amount of sample obtained with a compliant cavity procedure

name: spc.bulkDensSampleType
description: Soil sample consisting of a coherent, consolidated mass from a coring sampler, removed and placed in a bag. The core has a known volume and bagged sample is assumed to represent that volume. The actual volume depends on how carefully the core is trimmed
